handist.collections.dist

Class DistBag<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • handist.collections.dist.AbstractDistCollection
      • handist.collections.dist.DistBag<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the elements handled by the DistBag.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class DistBag<T>
extends AbstractDistCollection
    A class for handling objects at multiple places. It is allowed to add new elements dynamically. This class provides methods for load balancing.

    Note: In its current implementation, there are some limitations.

    • There is only one load balancing method
    • The method flattens the number of elements of the all places
    See Also:
